	lyn Keough Family Curator of Photography\, alongside Fractured Sublime by 
	Daniel Seth Kraus. Guests will have the opportunity to purchase signed cop
	ies of exhibiting artists’ books.\n\nhttps://www.edu.hcponline.org/events/
	opening-reception-hcp-annual-fellowship-exhibitions-and-daniel-seth-kraus\
