DESCRIPTION:Bad Astronaut & Photon Air Hockey Present \nAIR HOCKEY DOUBLES 
	TOURNAMENT\nEvery Thursday | 7:30 – 10 PM | Free Entry\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJoin u
	s every Thursday in the taproom for our exciting Air Hockey Tournaments! W
	hether you’re a beginner or an expert\, there’s a matchup for you. Enjoy t
